#SSH script to login to multiple servers and execute a command as SUDO
#multipath.sh
#./multipath.sh hostname.txt
#Save list of serves in hostname.txt and save it
#StrictHostKeyChecking=no doesnt prompt for RSA key host

#!/bin/bash
HOST="username"
PASS="secret"
while read line
do
    ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no $HOST@"$line" "hostname;echo "$PASS" | sudo -S /sbin/multipath -l;" < /dev/null
done < "$1"
